Italian brand Martinelli Luce takes inspiration from nature, minimalism and geometry for its lighting design. Explored conceptually in this new film by Diorama Studio, a whirlwind of emotions and colours transports us into the universe of the brand, delving into its rich history and drive towards innovation. For over 70 years, Martinelli Luce has elevated lighting design, the result of continuous technological research towards modern, functional and design solutions.⁣
