Saint Laurent's atmospheric new film – Summer of ’21, by Anthony Vaccarello – is directed by Paris-based Argentine filmmaker Gaspar Noe, and showcases the Women’s Summer 2021 collection. It features a remix of Donna Summer’s classic 'I Feel Love' by SebastiAn. 

Watch as icon of the swinging sixties, and Yves Saint Laurent muse, Charlotte Rampling is saluted by a new generation.

